We travel in packs and hit fast and hard. How is that not PvP? <br>
<br>
We always stop what we're doing to come to our friends Aid. How is that not PvP?<br>
<br>
10times mroe people show up after one of us dies....to CC naked Curse. We have 15 active members against a limitless stream of anti reinforcements. CRing is bitch when youre a PK, so if we can avoid a death, we will. Thats called living to fight another day.<br>
<br>
Wtf is your definition of Pvp? Duels?  Events? Arena? What?  <br>
<br>
And what the hell would 6 on 6 prove anyway?  Since when have any Curse (recently) declared themselves the ultimate in PvP.  We're PKs. Our goal is distruption not honor. <br>
<br>
Anway, if you care so little, don't play with us. There are plenty of zones.<br>
<br>
- Serraghost<br>
